snippet: Jozy Altidore broke Clint Dempsey’s record for most goals by an American in a European club season.
abstract: Soccer's Jozy Altidore breaks Clint Dempsey’s record for most goals by an American in a European club season, scoring his 24th in AZ Alkmaar’s 2-1 loss at RKC Waalwijk in Dutch league.
lead_paragraph: Jozy Altidore broke Clint Dempsey’s record for most goals by an American in a European club season.

headline.seo: Jozy Altidore Passes Clint Dempsey in Goals by American in European Club Season
headline.main: Altidore Passes Dempsey in Goals by American in European Club Season
